<emphasis box="[603,774,1581,1604]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="183">As long as uncus</emphasis>
2) 
<emphasis box="[807,997,1581,1604]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="183">Longer than uncus</emphasis>
.
</td>
</tr>
